title: OCS Fantasy bracket results!
body:
http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/sites/default/files/styles/scale_xlarge/public/upload/challenger_announce1.jpg?itok=KGj_Haq9

With the Oceanic Challenger Series concluding last night we can now see who has won our [fantasy bracket competition!](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/esports/JdybYApl-ocs-fantasy-bracket)

Congratulations to Absolute for making it into split 2 of the Oceanic Pro League, what a great best of 3!

The below players have been contacted on Facebook by [myself](https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100006763489424).
Congratulations to the only 4 players who won a 10 win IP boost AND Arclight Vel'Koz:
http://i.imgur.com/t8mAW5j.jpg

You can check out a ladder of the top 30 [here!](https://www.facebook.com/LeagueOfLegendsOceania?sk=app_36495350702&brandloc=DISABLE&app_data=chk-5525bebef040e)

Don't forget to check out the split 1 [Oceanic Pro League Finals](http://oce.lolesports.com/articles/opl-final-thursday) tonight!
